---
model: googleai/gemini-1.5-flash-latest
config:
  temperature: 0.9
  safetySettings:
  - category: HARM_CATEGORY_HATE_SPEECH
    threshold: BLOCK_NONE
  - category: HARM_CATEGORY_DANGEROUS_CONTENT
    threshold: BLOCK_NONE
  - category: HARM_CATEGORY_HARASSMENT
    threshold: BLOCK_NONE
  - category: HARM_CATEGORY_SEXUALLY_EXPLICIT
    threshold: BLOCK_NONE

input:
  type: object
  properties:
    name: 
      type: string
    lifestyle:
      type: string
      enum: 
        - SEDENTARY
        - ACTIVE
        - HECTIC
    country:
      type: string
      enum: 
        - INDIA
        - ITALIAN
        - AMERICAN
    flexiNutritionPreferences:
      type: object
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
          enum:
            - VEGETARIAN
            - NON_VEGETARIAN
            - VEGAN
        allergies:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        dietaryRestrictions:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        spicePreferences:
          type: number
        sweetOrHotPreferences:
          type: number
    levelOfCooking:
      type: string
      enum:
        - BEGINNER
        - INTERMEDIATE
        - ADVANCED
    favouriteFoodItems:
      type: array
      items:
        type: string
    healthGoals:
      type: array
      items:
        type: string
    healthIssues:
      type: array
      items:
        type: string
    healthMetrics:
      type: array
      items:
        type: object
        properties:
          weight:
            type: number
          height:
            type: number
          waterPercentage:
            type: number
            nullable: true
          fatPercentage:
            type: number
            nullable: true
          boneMass:
            type: number
            nullable: true
          calories:
            type: number
            nullable: true
    budget : 
      type : number
output:
  type: object
  properties:
    menu:
      type: array
      dayofweek :
        type : array
        items:
          type: object
          properties:
            category:
              type: string
            items:
              type: array
              items:
                type: object
                properties : 
                  name : 
                    type : string
                  ingredients : 
                    type : array
                  cutlery :
                    type : array
                  recipe : 
                    type : array
                  macroNutrientIndex :
                    type : object
                    properties :
                      nutritient : 
                        type : string
                      value : 
                        type : string
              
                        
--- 
`
Generate a menu suggestion for a week except sunday (cheat day) for {{name}} who has a {{lifestyle}} lifestyle. 
Their preferred nutrition type is {{flexiNutritionPreferences.type}}, and they have allergies to 
{{flexiNutritionPreferences.allergies}}, and dietary restrictions of 
{{flexiNutritionPreferences.dietaryRestrictions}}. 
They are at a {{levelOfCooking}} level of cooking. 
They are living in {{country}} country.
Their favourite foods include {{favouriteFoodItems}}.
They have the following health goals: {{healthGoals}}, and health issues: {{healthIssues}}. 
They have the following health metrics: {{healthMetrics}}
Give ingredients used to generate the menu should be less than the week wise budget: {{budget}}, based on their prices in {{country}}.
Make sure the output for every food item in the menu, recipe & macro-nutritients with their values as strings, contains the ingredients and cutlery & utensils used to prepare this recipe.


Output must be in JSON format.
`